---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Services | Wet Dog Drones"
  description="Construction progress monitoring, pre-construction documentation, volumetric analysis, and 3D modeling for Colorado construction projects.">

  <section class="bg-slate-900 text-white py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Services That Pay for Themselves</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300">Decision-grade data, 24–48 hour turnaround, Procore-compatible deliverables.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      
      <!-- Progress Monitoring -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <span class="text-4xl">📅</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Bi-Weekly Progress Flights</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-4">
          We establish a baseline before anyone steps on site. Then we return every two weeks with decision-grade orthomosaics, 3D models, and timeline comparisons.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600">
          <li>✓ Orthorectified maps (2D and 3D)</li>
          <li>✓ Timeline comparisons showing week-over-week progress</li>
          <li>✓ Automated change detection between flights</li>
          <li>✓ 24–48 hour delivery</li>
          <li>✓ Scale back to monthly after dry-in</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <hr class="my-12 border-slate-200" />

      <!-- Pre-Construction Documentation -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <span class="text-4xl">📸</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Pre-Construction Documentation</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-4">
          Before the first shovel hits dirt, we document existing conditions. Road damage, interior fixtures, site conditions — all timestamped and georeferenced.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-500 p-6 my-6">
          <p class="font-semibold text-amber-900">Real Result: $40,000 saved at Severance Library</p>
          <p class="text-amber-800 mt-2">Our pre-construction baseline proved existing road damage before construction began. The city claimed $80K in damage; we split it to $40K. "I was the hero because I saved a big chunk of money."</p>
        </div>
        
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600">
          <li>✓ Exterior site documentation (roads, curbs, landscaping)</li>
          <li>✓ Interior condition documentation</li>
          <li>✓ All data georeferenced and timestamped</li>
          <li>✓ Metadata that holds up in disputes</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <hr class="my-12 border-slate-200" />

      <!-- Interior Documentation -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <span class="text-4xl">🏢</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Interior Documentation</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-4">
          84,000 square feet. 20 hours on site. Every fixture, every radiator, every piece of copper — mapped and documented before construction crews arrive.
        </p>
        
        <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-500 p-6 my-6">
          <p class="font-semibold text-green-900">Real Result: $400,000 change order avoided at Clear Creek Schools</li>
          <p class="text-green-800 mt-2">When thieves stole copper before construction started, the GC tried to pin a $400K change order on FP. Our interior documentation proved the building was empty when we arrived. The GC ate the cost.</p>
        </div>

        <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600">
          <li>✓ Complete interior mapping with RTK accuracy</li>
          <li>✓ Every fixture, pipe, and component documented</li>
          <li>✓ Photo-verified point clouds</li>
          <li>✓ Proof that stands up in arbitration</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <hr class="my-12 border-slate-200" />

      <!-- Volumetric Analysis -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <span class="text-4xl">📊</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Volumetric Analysis & 3D Modeling</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-4">
          Cut/fill calculations, stockpile measurements, BIM-ready point clouds. Compatible with Procore, Autodesk, and your VDC workflow.
        </p>
        
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600">
          <li>✓ Cut/fill volume calculations</li>
          <li>✓ Stockpile measurements and tracking</li>
          <li>✓ BIM-ready point clouds (.las, .e57, .rcp)</li>
          <li>✓ Procore and Autodesk integration</li>
          <li>✓ Orthophotos with high-precision accuracy</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <hr class="my-12 border-slate-200" />

      <!-- Deliverables -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">What You Get</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">📁 Data Files</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-slate-600">
              <li>• Orthomosaics (GeoTIFF)</li>
              <li>• Point clouds (.las, .e57)</li>
              <li>• 3D mesh models (.obj, .fbx)</li>
              <li>• DEM / DTM rasters</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">🎥 Video Deliverables</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-slate-600">
              <li>• Progress time-lapses</li>
              <li>• 3D flythroughs</li>
              <li>• Marketing footage</li>
              <li>• Custom angles on request</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">📊 Reports</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-slate-600">
              <li>• Progress comparison reports</li>
              <li>• Volume calculations</li>
              <li>• Change detection analysis</li>
              <li>• Executive summaries</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">🔌 Integrations</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-slate-600">
              <li>• Procore</li>
              <li>• Autodesk (BIM 360, Revit)</li>
              <li>• Bluebeam</li>
              <li>• Custom API available</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-16">
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 transition text-lg inline-block">
          Get a Quote for Your Project
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
